description: Eamon Ryan defeats the deputy leader of the party, Catherine Martin, by a narrow margin.
title: Irish Green Party: Eamon Ryan wins leadership contest
title_page: Irish Green Party: Eamon Ryan wins leadership contest - BBC News
maintext: In May 2020, as talks to form a new government in Dublin were heating up, it emerged Ms Martin had been approached by some councillors in the party to stand for the leadership.
